company_name: SOLAN KRAFTFUTTERWERK SCHMALWIESER GESELLSCHAFT M.B.H. & CO KOMMANDITGESELLSCHAFT
information: The company SOLAN KRAFTFUTTERWERK SCHMALWIESER GESELLSCHAFT M.B.H. & CO KOMMANDITGESELLSCHAFT, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1900, which operates in the Feeds for animal farming industry. It is based in Bachmanning, Austria.
